{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake-gtest, ament-cmake-ros, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, lifecycle-msgs, osrf-testing-tools-cpp, rcl-lifecycle, rclc, std-msgs }:
